{
  "stem": "25651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My brother Henry went illegally, after the Germans occupied Czechoslovakia, across the border into Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Poland wasn't attacked yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he left with the last ship out of Poland to England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] had an arrangement with Leo that the next night, Leo would put us two on the same train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a wagons train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a [? rail-woman ?] who would take us across the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he phoned, and he said, it's all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Do it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] Now, Henry was saying to his elder brother, Leo, to kidnap me and, and [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Melosh ?], and take us across the border to Poland so that he would then pick us up and organize us to all go too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, my mother would come on the third night with Leo, because once the children would be gone, Henry said she would follow the children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Leo wasn't like Henry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leo wouldn't disobey Mom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] when Henry was dying, poor chap, a year and a half ago, the last two weeks, he was talking about nothing else.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just about this, that why didn't Leo kidnap us?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, because we would have saved the whole family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because Henry felt, you know, that he saved himself, because he went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then Leo said, well, I'm not coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leo said I'm not coming, because he told Mother I'll take the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Mother said, no, you won't, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I wasn't there at that discussion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So my mother-- you know, there were lots of events that took place, which I wasn't privy to, but which I know happened.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
